              "free_text": [
                "",
                "The cross sections of monitor reaction were defined by",
                "interpolation of the evaluated values of the reference",
                "from \"Physik Daten - Physics Data, Evaluation of Cross",
                "Sections for 14 Important Neutron-Dosimetry Reactions.",
                "Fachinformationszentrum Karlsruhe, Gesellschaft fur",
                "wissenschaftlich-technische Information mbH, Federal",
